name: EUME Classic Cabin 55cm Luggage
description: The Eume luggage is expertly crafted from 100% german bayer recycled polycarbonate, ensuring exceptional durability and resilience. This material offers three key benefits: it is remarkably lightweight, impervious to chemical and temperature extremes, and highly resistant to cracking. Functionality is a paramount feature, with a telescopic trolley handle incorporating a three-stage opening and closing mechanism. The luggage also includes retractable hand-carry handles on each side, capable of lifting weights up to 10 kg for cabin-sized luggage. The sides of the luggage serve a dual purpose: protecting it from scratches when stationary and doubling as hooks for small bags during transit. The silent-run pro double wheels, powered by Hinomoto Japanese technology, ensure smooth and silent handling across any terrain. Security is a top priority, facilitated by TSA-approved combination locks, providing peace of mind while traveling. The TSA lock even includes A and C type charging slots and a power bank pocket, along with internal slots. An antitheft zipper mechanism from SBS further safeguards belongings from unauthorized access. Inside, the luggage offers superior organization with two compartments: one secured by a zipper closure with a zipper pocket on top, and the other featuring a compression pad with a spill-proof zipper pocket and a net zipper pocket for essentials and toiletries. The compression pad serves a triple purpose: it acts as storage for small essentials, keeps clothing in place, and can be hung in hotel rooms with a hook on the back, ensuring toiletries or other items remain organized and accessible only when needed. The luggage is lined with high-quality, water-resistant polyester blend fabric and features mesh for ventilation. Additionally, there is space for customization of up to 10 characters, making it easy to identify your luggage and adding a personal touch to your Eume luggage. Overall, Eume luggage combines cutting-edge materials and thoughtful design to offer a superior travel experience Size : Capacity : 40 Liters Dimensions (L*B*H) : Centimeters: 37 cm x 22 cm x 55 cm Weight : 3.02 Kgs Material : Polycarbonate

SOME BY MI - AHA, BHA, PHA 30 Days Miracle Cream
description: Made In Korea DETAILS The Some By Mi AHA BHA PHA 30 Day Miracle Cream is a mild cream that repairs and strengthens your skin barrier. With 70.7% Centella Asiatica Extract (700,000 ppm) the cream ensures your skin is protected against external factors that can irritate it, and also helps restore a damaged skin barrier. Formulated with four key ingredients of Centella Asiatica, the Miracle Cream provides 4-Cica care, that calms redness and inflammation. A lightweight cream, it is also suitable for sensitive and acne-prone skin. AHA, BHA and PHA have different molecular sizes which allow them to work both on the surface and deeper within your skin to remove dead skin buildup, unclog pores, reduce moisture loss and hyperpigmentation. It also uses a patented ingredient, the Beautiful Herb Story-Complex, which uses 4 calming ingredients - Lavender, Rosemary, Thyme, and Oregano. Centella and Tea Tree Leaf Water also help with soothing the skin, as well as controlling excess oiliness. The Complex also provides antioxidant benefits and helps repair skin damage. Adenosine and Niacinamide help target fine lines and wrinkles, as well as reduce dullness. For best results, use it along with the rest of the AHA BHA PHA 30 Days Miracle Line. FUNCTION - A multi-purpose moisturizer with 4-Cica Care that soothes and repairs the skin barrier - AHA, BHA and PHA gently exfoliate to help brighten, clear pores, and control oil production - Centella Asiatica Extracts and Tea Tree Leaf Water soothe irritated skin - Lightweight cream, suitable for sensitive and acne-prone skin too Key Ingredients Centella Asiatica Extract: 70.78% Gotu Kola/ Centella Asiatica extract, helps calm breakouts, soothe redness and boost skin repair. The extract also consists of Madecassoside, Madecassic Acid, Asiaticoside, and Asiatic Acid. AHA: The cream uses Citric Acid (11ppm) to help remove dead skin and reduce hyperpigmentation. AHAs also help improve fine lines and reduce premature signs of aging. BHA: Salicylic Acid (100 ppm) helps unclog pores and control sebum production, while also clearing blackheads and whiteheads. Salix Alba (Willow) Bark Water is a naturally occurring source of salicylate (that can be converted to Salicylic Acid) and acts like a BHA as it clears your pores and minimizes their appearance. It is also anti-inflammatory and soothes the skin. PHA: Lactobionic acid (100 ppm) is a gentle exfoliant that reduces moisture loss and helps clear skin. Tea Tree Leaf Extract: 10,000 ppm tea tree leaf extract helps clear acne triggers and soothe the skin. Plant Extracts: Also uses a number of soothing, repairing, and moisturizing plant extracts. For instance, Neem Extract helps clarify the skin and treat acne and scars, while ingredients such as Licorice Root Extract, or Rice extract help brighten skin.
